Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:04.37,Tensei op CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,250)}曾经见过无数次的那一梦黄粱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:16.30,Tensei op JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(280,250)}君の割れた硝子細工{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:16.30,Tensei op CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(280,250)}被你摔碎的玻璃装潢
